Package com.irurueta.navigation.frames

Class NEDFrame

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.irurueta.navigation.frames.NEDFrame
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Frame, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable
    public class NEDFrame
extends java.lang.Object
implements Frame, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable
    Contains position, velocity and coordinates transformation matrix expressed in NED frame. Position is expressed as latitude, longitude and height. Velocity of body frame is expressed with respect ECEF frame and resolved along north, east and down axes, as defined in FrameType.LOCAL_NAVIGATION_FRAME.
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
